  ],
  "remarks": "LLC TRIMIX manufactures electronic warfare systems and anti-UAV (unmanned aerial vehicle) systems. The company’s products (including drone detectors Bulat) are used by the Russian military in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine. The drone detector Bulat has been tested by the Main Directorate of Innovative Development of the Ministry of Defence of the Russian Federation. The company’s electronic warfare systems and anti-UAV systems are officially purchased by the Ministry of Defence of the Russian Federation. Therefore, LLC TRIMIX is supporting actions which undermine and threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence of Ukraine, and is supporting and benefitting from the Government of the Russian Federation, which is responsible for the annexation of Crimea and the destabilisation of Ukraine.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}